---
import SEMLayout from '../../layouts/SEMLayout.astro'
import SEMHero from '../../components/sem/SEMHero.astro'
import SEMCTASection from '../../components/sem/SEMCTASection.astro'
---

<SEMLayout
  title="Smithwood Builders â€” Case Study"
  description="Digital marketing strategy driving growth for a premier home builder."
>
  <SEMHero
    label="Case Study"
    title="Smithwood Builders"
    subtitle="Digital marketing strategy driving growth for a premier home builder"
  />

  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-medium text-heading">Overview</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        Smithwood Builders is a custom home builder with a reputation for quality craftsmanship. Looking to expand their reach and grow their brand in an increasingly competitive housing market, they needed a strategic partner to develop their digital presence and generate qualified leads from prospective home buyers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Challenge -->
  <section class="bg-bg-light px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-medium text-heading">The Challenge</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        Reaching new home buyers in a competitive market requires more than just a website. Smithwood Builders needed to stand out among established competitors, communicate the quality of their craftsmanship, and connect with buyers who were actively searching for their dream home. The challenge was creating a digital marketing strategy that would generate measurable results while building long-term brand equity.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach -->
  <section class="px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-medium text-heading">Our Approach</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        We developed a comprehensive brand position strategy and executed a targeted digital marketing campaign tailored to Smithwood's ideal customer profile. Our approach combined compelling storytelling about their craftsmanship with data-driven digital marketing tactics, including search engine optimization, targeted advertising, and content marketing that showcased their portfolio of completed homes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results -->
  <section class="bg-bg-light px-6 py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="font-accent text-h2 font-medium text-heading">Results</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white p-6 shadow-card text-center">
          <p class="font-accent text-h1 font-bold text-teal-solid">30%</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-body">Increase in Enrollments</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white p-6 shadow-card text-center">
          <p class="font-accent text-h1 font-bold text-teal-solid">Stronger</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-body">Brand Identity</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-body-lg leading-relaxed text-text-body">
        The targeted digital marketing campaign delivered a 30% increase in enrollments, significantly exceeding Smithwood's growth targets. Beyond the numbers, the brand position strategy created a stronger, more recognizable identity that continues to differentiate Smithwood Builders in the market.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SEMCTASection
    title="Have a Similar Challenge?"
    description="Let's discuss how we can help your brand grow."
    ctaText="Start a Conversation"
    ctaHref="/contact"
  />
</SEMLayout>
